summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit to condemn private property for the laying off, opening, widening, extending and establishing of Beacon Avenue, et al, under Ordinance No. 30071, Cause No. 93467, insofar as the same affects certain property in blocks 11 and 12, T. I. McKinney's Plat of Central Seattle, an addition to the City of Seattle; in blocks 71 and 72, Colelge Grounds Addition to the City of Seattle; in block 73, McNaught's Plat of Central Seattle, an addition to the City of Seattle; in tract 10, McNaught's Supplemental Tract of Central Seattle, an addition to the City of Seattle; in block 5, Walker's Addition to the City of Seattle; in blocks 6, 7, 8, 9, 12, 13 and 17, Beacon Hill View Addition to the City of Seattle; and in blocks 2 and 3, Dunlap's Supplemental Addition to the City of Seattle.
